Charts.Name: Clients Last Backup Status
Charts.CommandText: SELECT       'Today' AS BackupStatus, 1 AS Position, COUNT(*) AS COUNT                      FROM            Net_Clients                      WHERE        (DATEDIFF(DD, LastBackupTime, GETDATE()) = 0)                      UNION ALL                      SELECT      '1 to 3 Days ago' , 2, COUNT(*)                      FROM            Net_Clients                      WHERE        (DATEDIFF(DD, LastBackupTime, GETDATE()) BETWEEN 1 AND 3)                      UNION ALL                      SELECT      '4 to 7 Days ago', 3, COUNT(*)                      FROM            Net_Clients                      WHERE        (DATEDIFF(DD, LastBackupTime, GETDATE()) BETWEEN 4 AND 7)                      UNION ALL                      SELECT       'More than 1 Week', 4, COUNT(*)                      FROM         Net_Clients                      WHERE        (DATEDIFF(DD, LastBackupTime, GETDATE()) > 7)                      ORDER BY 2

Charts.Name: Malware Types Detected in Last 7 Days
Charts.CommandText: SELECT       dbo.Date(Net_Rpt_Threats.ReceivedTime) AS Date_ReceivedTime, dbo.[AbrvValue](Net_Rpt_Threats.MalwareName,N'.',2) AS Abrv2_MalwareName, COUNT(*) AS COUNT                      FROM            Net_Rpt_Threats                      WHERE        (7 >= DATEDIFF(DD, Net_Rpt_Threats.ReceivedTime, GETDATE())) AND (dbo.[AbrvValue](Net_Rpt_Threats.MalwareName, N'.', 2) IN                      (SELECT        TOP (5) dbo.[AbrvValue](MalwareName, N'.', 2)                      FROM            Net_Rpt_Threats                      WHERE        (7 >= DATEDIFF(DD, ReceivedTime, GETDATE()))                      GROUP BY dbo.[AbrvValue](MalwareName, N'.', 2)                      ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC))                      GROUP BY dbo.Date(Net_Rpt_Threats.ReceivedTime),dbo.[AbrvValue](Net_Rpt_Threats.MalwareName, N'.', 2)                      ORDER BY 1,2
Charts.Text: Malware Types Detected in Last 7 Days

Charts.Name: Top Users with Detection Events in Last 7 Days
Charts.CommandText: SELECT   Net_Rpt_Threats.AppUser AS Net_Rpt_Threats_AppUser, Net_ClientGroups.Name AS Net_ClientGroups_Name, COUNT(*) AS COUNT                      FROM            Net_Rpt_Threats LEFT OUTER JOIN                      Net_Clients ON Net_Rpt_Threats.ClientID = Net_Clients.ClientID LEFT OUTER JOIN                      Net_ClientGroups ON Net_Clients.GroupID = Net_ClientGroups.GroupID                      WHERE        (7 >= DATEDIFF(DD, Net_Rpt_Threats.ReceivedTime, GETDATE())) AND (NOT (Net_Rpt_Threats.AppUser = 'Idle Scanner')) AND (NOT (Net_Rpt_Threats.AppUser = 'NT AUTHORITY\\SYSTEM')) AND (NOT (Net_Rpt_Threats.AppUser = '-'))                      GROUP BY Net_Rpt_Threats.AppUser, Net_ClientGroups.Name                      ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
Charts.Text: Top Users with Detection Events in Last 7 Days

Charts.Name: Anti-Crypto Detection in Last 7 Days
Charts.CommandText: SELECT        dbo.Date(Net_Rpt_AntiCrypto.ReceivedTime) AS Date_ReceivedTime, COUNT(*) AS COUNT                      FROM            Net_Rpt_AntiCrypto                      WHERE        (7 >= DATEDIFF(DD, Net_Rpt_AntiCrypto.ReceivedTime, GETDATE()))                      GROUP BY dbo.Date(Net_Rpt_AntiCrypto.ReceivedTime)                      ORDER BY 1

Charts.Name: Top Malwares
Charts.CommandText: SELECT        TOP(10) dbo.[AbrvValue](Net_Rpt_Threats.MalwareName,'.',3) AS Abrv3_MalwareName, COUNT(*) AS COUNT                      FROM            Net_Rpt_Threats                      GROUP BY dbo.[AbrvValue](Net_Rpt_Threats.MalwareName,'.',3)                      ORDER BY 2 DESC

Charts.Name: Top Infected Clients in Last 7 Days
Charts.CommandText: SELECT   Net_Rpt_Threats.ClientName AS Net_Rpt_Threats_ClientName, Net_ClientGroups.Name AS Net_ClientGroups_Name, COUNT(*) AS COUNT                      FROM            Net_Rpt_Threats LEFT OUTER JOIN                      Net_Clients ON Net_Rpt_Threats.ClientID = Net_Clients.ClientID LEFT OUTER JOIN                      Net_ClientGroups ON Net_Clients.GroupID = Net_ClientGroups.GroupID                      WHERE        (7 >= DATEDIFF(DD, Net_Rpt_Threats.ReceivedTime, GETDATE())) AND (NOT (Net_Rpt_Threats.AppUser = 'Idle Scanner')) AND (NOT (Net_Rpt_Threats.AppUser = 'NT AUTHORITY\\SYSTEM'))                      GROUP BY Net_Rpt_Threats.ClientName, Net_ClientGroups.Name                      ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
Charts.Text: Top Infected Clients in Last 7 Days
